ActExport and Import Permits Act
SubjectExport Permits Regulations (Non-strategic Products)
PrecisEXPORT PERMITS REGULATIONS (NON-STRATEGIC PRODUCTS) in order to require information from applicants for export permits for non-strategic goods, including Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement Origin Quota goods, similar to the Export Permit Regulations and the Import Permit Regulations, but with small differences to account for the nature of non-strategic goods (i.e. high-sugar-containing products and vehicles).
